name: Black and gold hair bow
description:
Gorgeous Black and gold hair bow, fastened by a subtle matching hair grip, this is a cheap way to jazz up your hair for a funky and fashionable look.

I literally only have 2 of these in stock and unless you request more then i wont be making anymore. We want our products to be as one of a kind as possible, but how can we say no if you really want it???

Feel free to contact me with any questions about our designs and stock.

name: Alexander Henry skulls and roses coin purse/ make up bag
description: This sexy purse/ make up bag is made from black felt and Alexander Henry skulls and roses printed cotton, with a swish red zip to match. This product is one of a kind, however if you like this design contact me and i will gladly design you your own personalised version of this fabulous coin purse/ make up bag.

name: White pearls, beaded charm bracelet
description: Beautiful one of a kind white pearls, beaded charm bracelet; comes with 3 gold decorative bangles. These gold metal charms consist of peace signs, angel wings and feathers and look beautiful with most outfits. This product is one of a kind, however if you like this design contact me and i will gladly design you your own personalised version of this beautiful beaded charm bracelet.

name: Ace of spades and Leopard print peace out brooches
description: Ace of spades; this super cool broach is made from metal and is very light weight. The clasp is also set at the back facing downwards to prevent it falling off. Leopard print peace out bow; secured with the same brooch clasp as the ace of spades, this funky and light hearted bow is decorated with colourful beading and a gold peace sign. These products are one of a kind, however if you like these designs contact me and i will gladly design you your own personalised version of these awesome brooches.

name: Pink and white pearls, beaded peace out necklace
description: This gorgeous necklace is made up of pink and white pearl beads, hung on a chain of cute tiny white beads. The pendant is a large gold peace sign (approx 3 x 3 cm). This product is one of a kind, however if you like this design contact me and i will gladly design you your own personalized version of this funky necklace.
